data.description: Welcome to The Lakes. This exquisite home, impeccably maintained by its original owners, offers a perfect blend of style and functionality. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a 3-car garage, the residence features both formal and informal dining areas, along with a formal living space and a family room adorned with tile floors and granite counters. The primary bedroom includes a mixed-use area that can effortlessly be transformed into a 5th bedroom. Additionally, the home offers a downstairs bedroom/den, catering to guests or family members who prefer convenient first-floor living. Enhancing its appeal, the home welcomes you with an open staircase with a chair lift and vaulted ceilings, creating a luminous and inviting atmosphere throughout. Ideally located in close proximity to Red Rock Casino, Downtown Summerlin, and the 215 Freeway, this property epitomizes both luxury and convenience.
